nchantment: Theater, Dance, Music, and the Visual Arts of the Middle East,</i> American University in Cairo Press, 2001, p. 375</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Rogers, S., \"Mohanna Durra,\" in <i>Mathaf Encyclopedia of Modern Art and the Arab World, Online: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.encyclopedia.mathaf.org.qa/en/bios/Pages/Mohanna-Durra.aspx\">http://www.encyclopedia.mathaf.org.qa/en/bios/Pages/Mohanna-Durra.aspx</a>; Mejcher-Atassi, S. and Schwartz, J.P., </i>Archives, Museums and Collecting Practices in the Modern Arab World,<i> Routledge, 2016, p.175</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Mejcher-Atassi, S. and Schwartz, J.P., <i>Archives, Museums and Collecting Practices in the Modern Arab World,</i> Routledge, 2016, p.175</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Mejcher-Atassi, S. and Schwartz, J.P., <i>Archives, Museums and Collecting Practices in the Modern Arab World,</i> Routledge, 2016, p.175</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Jordan National Art Gallery, <i>Photo Gallery,</i> Online: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.nationalgallery.org/PhotoGallery/tabid/59/Default.aspx\">http://www.nationalgallery.org/PhotoGallery/tabid/59/Default.aspx</a>; al- Mat\u1e25af al-Wa\u1e6dan\u012b, al-Urdunn\u012b lil-Fun\u016bn, al-\u01e6am\u012bla (\u02bbAmm\u0101n), Wi\u01e7d\u0101n \u02bbAl\u012b, <i>Jordan National Gallery of Fine Arts,</i>University of Michigan, 2009,  p.283</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1254\nCached time: 20180